          tanzania minister of water
        </p>
      </div>

      <section class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
        <div class="flex bg-white px-5 rounded-sm py-3 shadow-lg w-screen">
          <h3 class="font-light text-white bg-[#092958] px-4 py-2 rounded-md">
            Save Contact
